014</h2> <p> <strong><strong>Winner: </strong></strong><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/2014/mar/07/young-skins-review-debut-colin-barrett\">Young Skins</a> by Colin Barrett</p> <p><strong><strong>Shortlist:<br /></strong></strong><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/2014/jul/31/age-of-ambition-evan-osnos-review-china\">Age of Ambition</a> by Evan Osnos<br /><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/2014/mar/19/do-no-harm-brain-surgery-henry-marsh-review\">Do No Harm</a> by Henry Marsh<br /><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/2014/jan/24/night-guest-fiona-mcfarlane-review\">The Night Guest</a> by Fiona McFarlane<br /><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/2014/aug/05/guardian-first-book-award-2014-readers-choice-may-lan-tan\">Things to Make and Break by May-Lan Tan</a> (readers’ choice)</p> <h2> 2013</h2> <p> <strong><strong>Winner: </strong></strong><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/2013/nov/28/spinning-heart-donal-ryan-review\">The Spinning Heart</a> by Donal Ryan</p> <p> <strong><strong>Shortlist:<br /></strong></strong><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/2013/jun/20/need-new-names-bulawayo-review\">We Need New Names </a>by NoViolet Bulawayo<br /><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/2013/mar/06/sex-citadel-el-feki-review\">Sex and the Citadel</a> by Shereen El Feki<br /><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/2013/aug/31/burial-rites-hannah-kent-review\">Burial Rites</a> by Hannah Kent<br /><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/2013/jul/19/kiss-first-lottie-moggach-review\">Kiss Me First </a>by Lottie Moggach</p> <h2>2012</h2> <p> <strong><strong>Winner:</strong></strong> <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/2012/aug/31/the-yellow-birds-kevin-powers-review\">The Yellow Birds </a>by Kevin Powers</p> <p><strong><strong>Shortlist:<br /></strong></strong><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/2012/jul/29/tony-hogan-ice-cream-review\">Tony Hogan Bought Me an Ice-Cream Float Before He Stole My Ma </a>b